Paragraph Properties
<html>
<head>
<title>Paragraph properties</title>
<style type=”text/css”>
p
{
color:blue;
font-size:22px;
text-align:justify;
text-indent:300px;
line-height:30px;
border:3px solid red;
/*solid, dashed, dotted, double, groove, inset, outset */
margin:30px 20px 0px 40px;
padding:40px 20px 10px 30px;
/* margin means gap between the page and border 
padding means gap between the text and border */
}
</style>
</head>
<body>
<p>
Here are some text.
</p>
</body>
</html>

Scrollbar
